ks upon the problemthe Civilian Conservation Corps for idle young men the Public Works Administration for largescale projects to put lookers into jobs and the Federal Emergency Relief Administration for aiding state and local authorities in general direct relief n todays article President Roosevelt recounts the beginnings of the FERA and its development thru various stages into the pres ent WPA ARTICLE NUMBER FOUR Printed in The News Saturday March 28 In 1933 direct relief work was immediately necessary ko feed and clothe millions of our destitute and unem ployed citizens whose resources and means of livelihood had completely vanished during the years of depression When I first"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-09-28T04:56:55.839Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2020_now", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-8"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82016181/1938-03-26/ed-1/?sp=19", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_bullock_ver01:data:sn82016181:00516999639:1938032601:0871/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=329&w=222", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_bullock_ver01:data:sn82016181:00516999639:1938032601:0871/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=659&w=445", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_bullock_ver01/data/sn82016181/00516999639/1938032601/0871.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "washington", "washington d.c.", "district of columbia"], "location_city": ["washington"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_state": ["district of columbia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["5", "3", "0", "sn82016181", "1", "0000000019", "9", "6"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn82016181"], "number_page": ["0000000019"], "number_reel": ["0", 