retary Edison who today started the program to get them on the ways said the ordnance for the vessels will be construted at the naval gun factory here Two new destroyers will be built ene at the Puget Sound Navy Yard and the other at the Charleston S C Navy Yard at a combined cost of 9204295 while the New York Ship building Corp of Camden N J will construct a seaplane tender and a destroyer tender both to cost 20 680555 The private shipbuilder Mr Edison said in announcing the awards yesterday following consulta tion with President Roosevelt under bid estimates of the Norfolk and Philadelphia Navy Yards contrary to the case of the two new battleships The Assistant Secretary emphasized that the Navy is building these ships immediately in line with the Chief Executives desire that the Govern ment spend available funds now to assist business revival and to aid firms that build for the national defense ees LavotTs Halted The ultimate layoffs"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T06:38:23.689Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2018_2019", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-7"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045462/1937-12-08/ed-1/?sp=11", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1kahlo_ver01:data:sn83045462:00280601652:1937120801:0556/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=489&w=351", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1kahlo_ver01:data:sn83045462:00280601652:1937120801:0556/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=978&w=702", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_1kahlo_ver01/data/sn83045462/00280601652/1937120801/0556.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "washington", "washington d.c.", "district of columbia"], "location_city": ["washington"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_state": ["district of columbia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "applicati