ATION IS SIMILAR OVER FIFTH DISTRICT Norfolk Among Seven U S Cities With Gains Over Year Ago Baltimore Unchanged By EDWARD C STONE Trade in Washington department stores remained on an even keel dur ing the past week holding its own with the corresponding week last year the Commerce Department weekly review announced yesterday Similar conditions were reported in the rest of the fifth Federal Reserve district the trade status being better than in many centers outside this territory Business in the Capital was 116 per cent under the previous week No percentage comparison was made with the same period a year ago as there was so little difference in the trade levels Only one of the seven big department stores here reported a decrease from the 1937 sales total Trade conditions in the Capital are considered highly favorable as it will be recalled that the spring months of 1937 represented a peak period of business activity in the"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T06:38:36.478Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2018_2019", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-7"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045462/1938-02-20/ed-1/?sp=45", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601706:1938022001:0399/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=485&w=347", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601706:1938022001:0399/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=971&w=694", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02/data/sn83045462/00280601706/1938022001/0399.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "washington", "washington d.c.", "district of columbia"], "location_city": ["washington"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_state": ["district of columbia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "ap