 "description": ["CURB LIST GOES TO LOW LEVELS Leaders Decline Fractions to Around 3 Points in Mild Selling By th AitocUled Press VEW YORK Dec 23Leading curb chares were knor ked down frac I tions to around 3 points by moderate telling today Showing some resistance Lake Shore Mines Cord Corp and PanAmerican Airways crawled ahead fractionally In late trading SherwinWilliams was down 3 Newmont lost 2 and Bra liiian Traction and Aluminum Co gave up I each Fire Insurance Volumes to Show Moderate Gains P the Associated Press NEW YORK Dec 23Despite somewhat lower rates fire insurance companies generally are expected to report moderate gains in premium vol umes for 1937 a survey by Standard Statistics Co made public today said Automobile insurance has accounted for much of the gains although other lines have also improved Fire losses were 4 per cent lower for the first 10 months resulting in higher net un derwriting profits The survey expresses the opinion that with unfavorable business condi j tions in prospect for the first half of 1938 losses may well increase and volume of premiums decline i 1 i CURB BONDS DOMESTIC BONDS High Low Noon Ala Power 4is 67 82 82 82"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T06:38:30.388Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2018_2019", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-7"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045462/1937-12-23/ed-1/?sp=19", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601664:1937122301:0741/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=489&w=349", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601664:1937122301:0741/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=978&w=699", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02/data/sn83045462/00280601664/1937122301/0741.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 26, "language": ["engli