IN MIC DEATHS Charles Snyder Blamed in Crash Costing His and Wifes Lives A coroners jury this afternoon ex onerated Harry J Haynes 25yearold enior at George Washington Univer sity Medical School in the deaths of n elderly couple Injured fatally Christmas Eve when their automobile collided with his car on Mount Vernon boulevard Charles Snyder 75 of Springfield Va ho died yesterday in Emergency Hospital of injuries received in the collision was blamed by the jury for his own death and that of his wife T4 who was killed in the wreck Mr Haynes who lives at 707 Rock Creek Church road NW testified he werved his machine to the right of the highway in a futile effort to avoid the crash After completing the Snyder in fluest the jury turned to an inquiry into the death of Miss Mary Clement 66 of 223 Pennsylvania avenue SE who died Sunday in Providence Hos pital of injuries received Saturday when struck by an automobile at Thirteenth and D streets NE George H Hughes 21 of 622 Morton place NE was listed by police as driver Coroner A Magruder MacDonald also planned to perform an autopsy to determine whether Charles Rawlings"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T06:38:36.478Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2018_2019", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-7"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045462/1938-01-11/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601688:1938011101:0041/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=490&w=351", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02:data:sn83045462:00280601688:1938011101:0041/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=980&w=703", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_1lichtenstein_ver02/data/sn83045462/00280601688/1938011101/0041.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "washington",