idently think there was no mistake since the men are still in jail but noisy efforts to obtain their re lease have been the hottest kind of political appeal to the radical labor vote for two de cades and Benson is only following the ex ample of Floyd B Olson in his efforts TO MOST MINNESOTANS THE KIND of labor troubles we have had in Minnesota particularly Minneapolis and the current trouble there which led to the murder of"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-01-04T03:52:54.721Z", "group": ["ndnp/mnhi", "minnesota-historical-society-saint-paul-mn-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85025570/1937-12-09/ed-1/?sp=10", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_limbo_ver01:data:sn85025570:00383348390:1937120901:0612/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=291&w=233", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_limbo_ver01:data:sn85025570:00383348390:1937120901:0612/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=582&w=466", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_limbo_ver01:data:sn85025570:00383348390:1937120901:0612/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1165&w=932", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mnhi/batch_mnhi_limbo_ver01/data/sn85025570/00383348390/1937120901/0612.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 23, "language": ["english"], "location": ["redwood falls", "redwood", "united states", "redwood county", "minnesota"], "location_city": ["redwood falls"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["redwood"], "location_state": ["minnesota"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["3", "0", "0000000010", "1", "8", "4", "9", "sn85025570"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn85025570"], "number_page": ["0000000010"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "3", "8", "3", "3", "4", "8", "3", "9", "0"